data.description: Move-In Ready! Zoned For Horses!  Call Today to View this Amazing Property! Beautiful Inside & Out! Close to Everything and still Country!  This owner has done all the work for you! New in 2023: Roof, A/C, Fresh Paint Inside & Exterior and Outdoor Buildings. New Skirting has been installed with Key Door Access.  Bathroom 1 has a new sink, tub/shower, exhaust fan, plumbing fixtures and new light fixture.  New ceiling fans in both bedrooms and vinyl flooring throughout.  Kitchen includes many upgrades too! New refrigerator, farmhouse sink and faucet, push button garbage disposal, new Bluetooth glass top stove, and new Bluetooth All-in-One Washer/Dryer.  2nd Bath has a new pedestal sink, refinished tub/shower, and all new plumbing fixtures. You will fall in love with the outdoor living spaces, there are so many!  Enjoy the screened Gazebo complete with ceiling fan and outlets, Cook up great BBQ in your new outdoor Kitchen with an   in-cabinet stainless steel grill with mini frig.  A solar heated outdoor shower!  22x11 wood sun deck around your 22x54 above ground pool with sand filter and new dual pump.  Each outdoor area has its own breaker too!  Bring the Animals!  There is a 2 stall horse stable and tack room on-site as well as a 1.5 acre horse pasture.  Deep well with advanced filtration system.  Septic tank serviced January 2024.  Ease of entry with an Automatic Gate Opener with Key Pad that encloses the fully fenced yard.  There is even a "Catio" a screened outdoor enclosure which allows a cat access to the outside and back inside again as desired!  This is a Must See Property!
